{"tid":2439186,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"NOW工程人員採訪期間遭警暴 索償案下月開審 律政司無視法庭命令遲交文件","createTime":"2021-03-09T05:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T15:58:28.000Z","uid":240362,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d2f5e9aeff6b16c1c341771e9dd5be56d539b129","tid":2439186,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:17:48.000Z","msg":"Now新聞台工程人員李小龍2014年在佔旺區採訪期間，突遭警員搶走鋁梯，隨後反被指襲警被捕。李稱被捕期間遭多名警員按在地上拳打腳踢，身體多處受傷，出現創傷後壓力症狀，前年入稟區域法院向警方索償。案件即將於下月開審之際，代表警隊的律政司今被揭無視法庭命令，遲交文件達一個月之久。法官不滿，揚言不能期望原告一方能「奇蹟地」快速審閱文件及作出回應，下令負責本案的政府律師甚或更高層人士須於3天內致函法庭交代。<br />\n<br />\n案件今早作審前覆核，法官李樹旭指出，代表警方的被告律政司司長一方，遲遲未呈交審訊文件冊的編號索引，直至上周才完成並送達原告李小龍一方，比上次聆訊後法庭命令所要求的限期，足足遲了一個月。<br />\n<br />\n法官質疑律政司收到指示後是否擱在一旁不理，反問律政司怎能期望原告能「奇蹟地」（miraculously）對遲交的文件作出回應。法官揚言，若律政司無視命令，法庭下達命令也變得毫無意義。律政司代表回應稱是疏忽睇漏眼（oversight），法官不滿解釋，怒斥律政司一方謂：「訴訟不是這樣做的！你和我都知道。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210309/J6VBO3OVTREOHBQWA7BYMLJZQM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210309%2FJ6VBO3OVTREOHBQWA7BYMLJZQM%2F&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy62paxXJRTFpYESBXKIXFX0%3D&h=1eeb6631\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210309%2FJ6VBO3OVTREOHBQWA7BYMLJZQM%2F&h=6dc689f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210309/J6VBO3OVTREOHBQWA7BYMLJZQM/</a>"},{"pid":"0d93ab08823d04294f2bb2df9efb4612b7f6e45b","tid":2439186,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:18:22.000Z","msg":"律政司代表今天才在庭上提出，警員記事冊字迹難辨，「連我本人理解也有困難」，提出將警察記事冊內容繙譯成謄本，以便利審訊，獲法庭接納。<br />\n<br />\n至於原告一方自行將警員口供紙繙譯成英文，律政司一方聲稱繙譯版本差劣兼弄錯文法，一度要求採用經核證的繙譯本。法官閱讀文件後，指譯文雖不完美，但未至於令人不明白內容；又指譯文不是今天才出現，律政司早已閱讀，加上核證譯本需時，反問：「我們尚有不足一個月開審，現在又說有繙譯問題？」最終拒絕律政司申請。<br />\n<br />\n案件按原定排期將於4月8日開審，預計需時6天。散庭前，法官特意問各方還有沒有事項需要法庭下達指示，明言希望案件順利開審，「不要再有驚喜」。"},{"pid":"7be11bf212f522c76accedff9694599ea01d91e6","tid":2439186,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:18:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2459eccc29d0a6cf968c04ac964ff12ff4069f3a","tid":2439186,"uid":1654,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:19:34.000Z","msg":"now 都染紅都未審"},{"pid":"4330f741ed5a60caa0f1ee798393c31f8196486e","tid":2439186,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7be11bf212f522c76accedff9694599ea01d91e6","tid":2439186,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:18:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:19:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6212f0c6df53c1d80064026fe4acd28c808138f5","tid":2439186,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:22:25.000Z","msg":"Claim好大舊錢？要去到區域法院"},{"pid":"c78d0548612e65ee544cf04b70f3abf77e822641","tid":2439186,"uid":36152,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:22:49.000Z","msg":"三萬大過法庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家冇王法係正常，三萬話點就點，再嘈連法庭都拆埋你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d608